<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Reset Your Password - InvoDrop</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        color: #222;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 24px;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 32px 24px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }
      h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        color: #222;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4f8cff;
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        color: #888;
        font-size: 0.93em;
        margin-top: 32px;
      }
      .muted {
        color: #666;
      }
      .note {
        background: #f4f7ff;
        padding: 12px 16px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        border: 1px solid #e5ecff;
        margin: 16px 0;
        color: #2b3a67;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Hello <%= name %>!</h2>

      <p>
        A request was made to reset the password for your InvoDrop account. If
        this was you, click the button below to choose a new password.
      </p>

      <a href="<%= resetPasswordUrl %>" class="button" >Reset Your Password</a>

      <p>
        If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:
        <br />
        <a href="<%= resetPasswordUrl %>"><%= resetPasswordUrl %></a>
      </p>

      <p><strong>This link will expire in 1 hour.</strong></p>

      <div class="note">
        For security, this link can be used only once. If it expires or has
        already been used, start a new reset request from the sign-in page.
      </div>

      <p class="muted">
        If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this
        email—your password will not change.
      </p>

      <div class="footer">
        — The InvoDrop Team<br />
        Need help? Contact us.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
